data.description: Rare opportunity in highly sought-after Kensington Estates.  Beautiful landscaped property backs up to the heavily forested corps of engineers property providing plenty of privacy for the homeowners.  Stunning 4 bedroom, 3.5 bath, 3 car garage with hand scraped hardwoods, two living areas, game room, study, built-ins, plenty of storage, with walk out attic space.  Home features fresh paint, numerous upgrades, a gourmet kitchen with island and granite counter tops.  Downstairs master, family room, and dining area provide beautiful views of the incredible backyard with two decks, and direct access to hiking trails surrounding Lake Lewisville.  Perfect for entertaining and everyday living.
